          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "It is found that in electronuclear disintegration of",
                "the  Li-7 nuclei into tritium (t) and He-4 nuclei at",
                "excitation energies Eg<20 MeV reactions are observed",
                "in which besides t (En-t<6 MeV) and He-4 particles of",
                "the third kind are emitted. These may be photons  of",
                "energy Eg'=8 MeV. The cross section of possible",
                "reaction Li-7(e,t)He-4, gamma' is compatible to the",
                "cross section of common disintegration of Li-7 into two",
                "particles t and He-4: Li-7(e,t)He-4."
              ]
            }
          ],
